window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Alone on the battlefield. Surrounded by death. Cornered by enemies. And ready to die. </p> <p>Drizzt Do’Urden has become the Hunter, the bane of the orc hordes still ravaging the North. Cut off, alone, convinced that everything he ever valued has been destroyed, all that’s left is to kill, and kill, and kill, until there are no enemies left. But there are a lot of enemies, and even the Hunter is just one lone drow.</p>"; 
